{
  "stem": "23498.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She wrote a beautiful letter to them, said, we probably won't survive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I want you to adopt my son, who is a nice boy, and he'll do whatever you want him to, and that sort of letter-- they sent with him.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my brother went by tram.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where we were living.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, you know, from that street-- well, I don't remember, it was [INAUDIBLE] or some other street in [?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Krakow. ?] He knew [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Krakow ?] because we used to live there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he-- he asked, because he was a typical [YIDDISH], you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But being on the tram, he wasn't careful enough, and-- and the-- his friends, in a-- in a good faith, his school friends, were yelling, [INAUDIBLE], what are you doing here-- like by the name, but a softer name.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were calling him, and everyone could hear.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he already was careful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You see, for-- for instance, my brother wasn't-- was such an Aryan type that in the ghetto, he got hit by a German.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What are you doing here?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You go out of the ghetto and quick.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You see, he-- he didn't look-- So your brother was accepted, was adopted by this family?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then, I'm-- I'm coming to it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He went there, and they took him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took him, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was hidden in the factory, and he was there to the end.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But what an end.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then my mother left, because I still didn't want to-- I-- I didn't feel secure.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If my parents wouldn't be there, I didn't want to go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So my mother left, and my mother had another address, where there were poor people-- also clients.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They all were my father's clients.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my father knew that they hadn't got anything to live from.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
